snippet.title: [Procelio] "Deep Freeze" Update 1.4a
snippet.description:
Welcome back friends!

We know we've been quiet lately, but that's because we've been cooking up one massive update for you. A new weapon and a new map are headliners, but the real star of the show is the entire year we spent improving the quality of the game, fixing bugs, implementing new features, and improving performance. 

Check out the link below for just a surface level view of everything we've been up to.
https://proceliogame.com/changelogs/14a
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Music: Blade - Enro
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Visit our website: https://proceliogame.com/
